### Set environment variables
@host = http://localhost:8080/api/orders
@authToken = Bearer tu_token_aqui
@orderId = id_de_tu_orden_aqui
@page = 0

### 1. Crear nueva orden (POST)
POST {{host}}
//Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "PRESENTIAL",
  "waiterId": 1,
  "tableNumber": "Mesa 5",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "dish_id_example",
      "productType": "DISH",
      "notes": "Sin cebolla"
    }
  ]
}

### 2. Obtener todas las órdenes paginadas (GET)
GET {{host}}/{{page}}/page
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 3. Obtener detalle de una orden específica (GET)
GET {{host}}/{{orderId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 4. Actualizar una orden (PUT)
PUT {{host}}/{{orderId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS",
  "tableNumber": "Mesa 6"
}

### 5. Cancelar una orden (PATCH)
PATCH {{host}}/{{orderId}}/cancel
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 6. Eliminar una orden (DELETE)
DELETE {{host}}/{{orderId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}